WEBVTT

00:01.213 --> 00:02.202
Previously on Angel:

00:02.373 --> 00:06.605
When I was a higher being, I could
see everything you ever did as Angelus.

00:06.813 --> 00:09.373
I love you, Angel, but
I can't be with you.

00:09.573 --> 00:11.086
This is where you were born.

00:16.933 --> 00:20.892
You never had a family or
friends or anything that's real.

00:21.093 --> 00:25.371
-  And if this is the end, then I
want you to have something that is.

00:25.573 --> 00:28.610
Last night will always be
special, but it can't happen again.

00:28.813 --> 00:31.407
Take your new boyfriend and
get the hell out of here.

00:31.613 --> 00:32.682
- Get over it.
- What?

00:32.853 --> 00:35.003
There are bigger things at stake.

00:35.213 --> 00:37.044
Connor's scared you think
he's connected to the Beast.

00:37.253 --> 00:39.608
It does tend to show
up whenever he's around.

00:39.773 --> 00:40.842
-  We discovered the Beast's plan.

00:41.013 --> 00:42.890
To blot out the sun for all of eternity.

00:43.453 --> 00:45.011
-  The sun, it's gone.

00:45.173 --> 00:49.212
I had a vision of you, long ago, standing
in a field of bodies with the Beast.

00:50.013 --> 00:52.686
- This wasn't about Connor. It's about...
- Angelus.

00:52.853 --> 00:54.605
I don't know this Beast.

00:54.813 --> 00:57.566
But Angelus might. We need Angelus.

00:59.693 --> 01:00.808
Officials from...

01:00.973 --> 01:02.929
... the National Weather
Service remain baffled...

01:03.093 --> 01:05.891
... as to the cause of
this strange phenomenon.

01:06.053 --> 01:08.567
All that's being reported
at this mid-afternoon hour...

01:08.733 --> 01:12.282
... is what meteorologists are calling,
quote, "a localized abnormality"...

01:12.453 --> 01:16.332
... confirming earlier reports that
outlying areas remain unaffected...

01:16.533 --> 01:19.764
... while the sun over Los Angeles
has, for all intents and purposes...

01:19.933 --> 01:21.685
... been blotted out from the sky.

01:21.893 --> 01:25.124
The mayor's office scheduled a news
conference for 6:00 this evening...

01:25.293 --> 01:28.603
... regarding this bizarre development
and what it may mean for the city.

01:28.773 --> 01:30.570
-  I'll tell you what it means.

01:30.733 --> 01:33.691
As soon as vamps realize this
town's open for business 24/7...

01:33.893 --> 01:36.168
...there's gonna be a huge
rise in undead tourism.

01:36.333 --> 01:38.767
We just gotta find a way
to bring back the sun.

01:38.933 --> 01:42.562
Working on it. Failing
miserably, but working on it.

01:42.733 --> 01:46.567
I could really use some help
deciphering some of these symbols.

01:46.733 --> 01:50.043
Or all of them, really.

01:50.853 --> 01:53.447
I need Wesley.

01:54.333 --> 01:56.449
His expertise.

01:56.653 --> 01:58.803
Yeah, well, rogue warrior
took off without a word.

01:59.013 --> 02:02.244
After Electro-Gwen decided to skip
town when the going got tougher.

02:02.453 --> 02:04.330
Not big on the teamwork, either of them.

02:04.533 --> 02:06.330
You're wasting your time.

02:06.493 --> 02:08.050
"The answer is among us."

02:10.733 --> 02:13.406
He knows. He's part of the plan.

02:13.613 --> 02:16.173
- He doesn't remember.
- So he says.

02:16.333 --> 02:18.722
You saw him yourself,
making a pact with the Beast.

02:18.933 --> 02:21.401
It wasn't Angel in my
vision. It was Angelus.

02:21.613 --> 02:27.449
- He is Angelus.
- Believe me, you've never met Angelus.

02:28.853 --> 02:32.129
Me neither. But I'm starting
to think maybe it's time we did.

02:32.333 --> 02:36.121
Maybe Wes is right. Big Beastie has
got to be stopped, and I'm out of ideas.

02:36.333 --> 02:39.052
If there's a chance Angelus
has inside info we could use...

02:39.253 --> 02:41.084
You think he's going to turn it over?

02:41.293 --> 02:43.045
I think it's worth a try.

02:43.253 --> 02:47.166
Not gonna happen. The Gypsies cursed
him with a soul so he'd feel remorse...

02:47.333 --> 02:50.405
...to make him suffer for
all the people he slaughtered.

02:50.613 --> 02:55.846
Removing that soul is the only way
to change Angel back into Angelus.

02:56.053 --> 02:58.283
A lot easier said than done.

02:58.453 --> 03:00.091
-  The Gypsy curse was specific.

03:00.253 --> 03:03.484
For Angel to lose his soul, he
would have to experience a moment...

03:03.653 --> 03:07.123
...of perfect, pure happiness.

03:09.093 --> 03:14.884
And right now, happiness of any
kind is in kind of short supply.

03:15.093 --> 03:17.926
- You sure?
- Sorry, bucko, I got nothing.

03:18.133 --> 03:21.569
Your choice of "The Night the Lights
Went Out in Georgia" threw me a wee.

03:21.733 --> 03:24.122
I'm personally not huge
with the Vicky Lawrence love.

03:24.333 --> 03:27.564
Doesn't make sense. I remember
everything Angelus did, I did.

03:27.733 --> 03:31.692
Every family butchered, every child
slaughtered, every throat ripped out.

03:31.853 --> 03:34.162
I remember every detail of all of it.

03:34.373 --> 03:37.012
So how come you don't have a
smidge of any recollection...

03:37.173 --> 03:40.370
...of a giant magma demon
with ram horns and goat legs?

03:40.573 --> 03:43.883
Hey, all's I can tell you, stud, is
if it's in there, it's buried deep.

03:44.053 --> 03:45.805
Deep inside Angelus.

03:46.013 --> 03:48.481
Then that's where it stays.
Even if I wanted it...

03:48.653 --> 03:51.167
...there's no way to bring Angelus back.

